Cognate with {{cog|de|dünn}}, {{cog|nl|dun}}, {{cog|fy|tin}}, {{cog|is|þunnur}}, {{cog|da|tynd}}, {{cog|sv|tunn}}, {{cog|la|tenuis}}, {{cog|ga|tanaí}}, {{cog|cy|tenau}}, {{cog|lv|tievs}}, {{cog|sa|तनु|tr=tanú||thin}}, {{cog|fa|تنگ|tr=tang|t=narrow}}. {{doublet|en|tenuis}}. Also related to {{m|en|tenuous}}.

